                Date.prototype.to_iso_with_offset = function() {
                    var time_zone_offset = -this.getTimezoneOffset(),
                        time_zone_diff = time_zone_offset >= 0 ? '+' : '-',
                        pad = function(num) {
                            var norm = Math.floor(Math.abs(num));
                            return (norm < 10 ? '0' : '') + norm;
                        };
                    return this.getFullYear() +
                        '-' + pad(this.getMonth() + 1) +
                        '-' + pad(this.getDate()) +
                        'T' + pad(this.getHours()) +
                        ':' + pad(this.getMinutes()) +
                        ':' + pad(this.getSeconds()) +
                        time_zone_diff + pad(time_zone_offset / 60) +
                        ':' + pad(time_zone_offset % 60);
                }

                                Iowa State Advances to Sweet 16 With Win Over Wisconsin
                            </h3> <time datetime="item.date" class="sa-widgets-stories-related__item-time">5 days ago</time></div></a></article></li></ul> <a href="https://cyclones.com/sports/mbball/archives" class="sa-widgets-stories-related__more-link sa-widgets-stories-related__more-link--footer">More in News <span class="sa-widgets-stories-related__more-icon sf-arrows-circle-right"></span></a><div dir="ltr" class="resize-sensor" style="pointer-events: none; position: absolute; inset: 0px; overflow: hidden; z-index: -1; visibility: hidden; max-width: 100%;"><div class="resize-sensor-expand" style="pointer-events: none; position: absolute; inset: 0px; overflow: hidden; z-index: -1; visibility: hidden; max-width: 100%;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; transition: all 0s ease 0s; width: 1197px; height: 386px;"></div></div><div class="resize-sensor-shrink" style="pointer-events: none; position: absolute; inset: 0px; overflow: hidden; z-index: -1; visibility: hidden; max-width: 100%;"><div style="position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; transition: all 0s ease 0s; width: 200%; height: 200%;"></div></div></div></div></div>
                                        </div></div>
										
											                            </div>
																 
            <script>
                require(['vue', 'knockout', 'analytics', './components/v-content-ad'], function (Vue, ko, Analytics) {
                    Vue.config.devtools = true;
                    Vue.component('vue-roster-template-list', {
                        template: `
                            <div class="sidearm-roster-template-list">
                                <ul class="sidearm-roster-list reset-list" id="roster-players">
                                    <template v-for="(player, index) in computedPlayers" :key="player.rp_id">
                                        <div
                                            v-if="(index === 0 && hasMultipleGenders) || (index > 0 && player.gender !== computedPlayers[index - 1].gender)"
                                            class="sidearm-roster-list-gender-label"
                                        >
                                            <h3><span>{{ player.gender === 'M' ? "Men's" : "Women's" }} Team</span></h3>
                                        </div>
                                        <li class="sidearm-roster-list-item">
                                            <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-top-row">
                                                <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-link flex flex-align-center">
                                                    <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-photo">
                                                        <img v-if="player.image" class="sidearm-roster-list-item-photo-img" :src="player.image.path + '/' + player.image.filename + '?width=96&height=96&mode=crop&anchor=topcenter'" :alt="player.image.alt">
                                                        <div v-else style="width: 96px; height: 96px"></div>
                                                        <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-photo-number" v-if="(player.jersey_number || player.jersey_number_2)">
                                                            <span v-if="(player.jersey_number || player.jersey_number_2) && checkDisplayFields('roster_jerseynum', 'special_column')">{{ player.jersey_number_2 ? player.jersey_number_2 : player.jersey_number }}</span>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-info flex-item-1 flex flex-column medium-flex-row medium-flex-align-center">
                                                        <div class="flex-item-1">
                                                            <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-name sidearm-roster-player-name">
                                                                <a :href="'/sports/' + sport.global_sport_name_slug + '/roster/' + slugify(player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name) + '/' + player.rp_id">{{ player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name }}</a>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-meta">
                                                                <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-position" v-if="player.position_short && checkDisplayFields('rp_position_short', 'db_field')">{{ player.position_short }}</span>
                                                                <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-position" v-if="player.position_long && checkDisplayFields('rp_position_long', 'db_field')">{{ player.position_long }}</span>
                                                                <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-year" v-if="player.academic_year_short && checkDisplayFields('roster_class', 'special_column')">{{ player.academic_year_short }}</span>
                                                                <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-height" v-if="player.height_feet && checkDisplayFields('height', 'db_field')">{{ player.height_feet + "'" + ' ' + player.height_inches + '"' }}</span>
                                                                <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-weight" v-if="player.weight && player.gender != 'W' && checkDisplayFields('rp_weight', 'db_field')">{{ player.weight }}</span>
                                                                <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-custom3" v-if="player.custom3 && checkDisplayFields('rp_custom3','db_field')">{{ player.custom3 }}</span>
                                                                <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-major" v-if="player.major && checkDisplayFields('player_major','db_field')">{{ player.major }}</span>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="flex-item-1">
                                                            <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-hometown" v-if="player.hometown && (checkDisplayFields('player_hometown','db_field') || checkDisplayFields('hometownhighschool','db_field') || checkDisplayFields('hometownprevious','db_field'))">{{ player.hometown }}</div>
                                                            <div>
                                                                <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-highschool" v-if="player.highschool && (checkDisplayFields('player_highschool','db_field') || checkDisplayFields('hometownhighschool','db_field'))">{{ player.highschool }}</span>
                                                                <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-previous-school" v-if="player.previous_school && (checkDisplayFields('player_previous_school','db_field') || checkDisplayFields('hometownprevious','db_field'))">{{ player.previous_school }}</span>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <a class="sidearm-roster-list-item-bio hide-on-large text-left" :href="'/sports/' + sport.global_sport_name_slug + '/roster/' + slugify(player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name) + '/' + player.rp_id">
                                                            <span>Full Bio</span>
                                                            <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-arrows-circle-right sidearm-icon"></span>
												                            </a>
										                            </div>
                                                    <a class="sidearm-roster-list-item-bio hide-on-medium-down" :href="'/sports/' + sport.global_sport_name_slug + '/roster/' + slugify(player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name) + '/' + player.rp_id">
                                                        <span>Full Bio</span>
                                                        <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-arrows-circle-right sidearm-icon"></span>
								                            </a>
										                    </div>
										                    </div>
                                            <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-social" v-if="player.has_social_links">
                                                <a :href="'https://www.twitter.com/' + player.twitter_username" v-if="player.twitter_username">
                                                <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-twitter sidearm-icon">
                                                </span></a>
                                                <a :href="'https://www.instagram.com/' + player.instagram_username" v-if="player.instagram_username">
                                                <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-instagram sidearm-icon">
                                                </span></a>
                                                <a :href="'https://www.youtube.com/' + player.youtube_username" v-if="player.youtube_username">
                                                <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-youtube sidearm-icon">
                                                </span></a>
                                                <a :href="'https://www.twitch.com/' + player.twitch_username" v-if="player.twitch">
                                                <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-twitch sidearm-icon">
                                                </span></a>
                                                <a :href="'https://www.facebook.com/' + player.facebook_username" v-if="player.facebook_username">
                                                <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-facebook sidearm-icon">
                                                </span></a>
                                                <a :href="'https://www.tiktok.com/@' + player.tiktok_username" v-if="player.tiktok_username">
                                                <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-tiktok sidearm-icon">
                                                </span></a>
                                                <a :href="'https://www.cameo.com/' + player.cameo_username" v-if="player.cameo_username">
                                                <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-cameo sidearm-icon">
                                                </span></a>
									                    </div>
								                    </li>
                                        <div id="vue-content-ad" v-if="(index + 1) === parseInt(players.length / 2)">
                                            <content-ad :container_element="'roster-players'"  :vertical_ad=true ></content-ad>
							                        </div>
                                    </template>
									                        </ul>
                                <div class="sidearm-roster-staff-dfp" v-reapplyKnockout>
                                    <ads-component params="{name : 'dfp-leaderboard-standard'}" ></ads-component>
								                        </div>
							                        </div>
                        `,
                        props: {
                            displayFields: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Array,
                            },
                            players: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Array,
                            },
                            sport: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Object,
                            }
                        },
                        methods: {
                            checkDisplayFields(field, column_name) {
                                let _field = this.displayFields.find(f => f[column_name] === field)
							
                                if (_field) {
                                    return true;
                                }

                                return false;
                            },
                            slugify(text) {
                                return text.toString().toLowerCase()
                                    .replace(/\s+/g, '-')
                                    .replace(/[^\w\-]+/g, '')
                                    .replace(/\-\-+/g, '-')
                                    .replace(/^-+/, '')
                                    .replace(/-+$/, '');
                            },
                        },
                        computed: {
                            computedPlayers() {
                                return this.players.map(player => ({ ...player, has_social_links: player.cameo_username || player.facebook_username || player.instagram_username || player.snapchat_username || player.tiktok_username || player.twitch_username || player.youtube_username || false })) 
                            },
                            hasMultipleGenders() {
                                if (this.players.some(player => player.gender !== this.players[0].gender)) return true;
                                return false;
                            }
                        }
                    });
                    Vue.component('vue-roster-template-grid', {
                        template: `
                            <div class="sidearm-roster-template-grid" >
                                <table class="sidearm-roster-table" v-if="players.length">
                                    <caption class="sidearm-roster-table-caption hide">{{ $root.roster.title }}</caption>
                                    <thead class="sidearm-roster-table-head hide-on-medium-down">
                                        <tr class="sidearm-roster-table-row">
                                            <th
                                                v-for="(field, index) in displayFields"
                                                :key="index"
                                                @click="sortByField(field.db_field ? field.db_field : field.special_column)"
                                                class="sidearm-roster-table-heading"
                                            >
                                                {{ field.title }}
                                                <span
                                                    v-if="activeField && activeField[0] === (field.db_field ? field.db_field : field.special_column)"
                                                    class="sidearm-icon"
                                                    :class="{
                                                        'sf-arrows-thick-down': activeField[1] === 'desc',
                                                        'sf-arrows-thick-up': activeField[1] === 'asc'
                                                    }"
                                                ></span>
                                            </th>
                                                </tr>
                                            </thead>
                                    <tbody class="sidearm-roster-table-body" id="roster-players">
                                        <template v-for="(player, index) in playersSorted" :key="player.rp_id">
                                            <tr class="sidearm-roster-table-row">
                                                <td class="sidearm-roster-table-data" v-for="(field, index) in displayFields" :key="index" v-html="getPlayerFieldValue(player, field.db_field ? field.db_field : field.special_column)"></td>
                                                            </tr>
                                            <tr id="vue-content-ad" v-if="(index + 1) === parseInt(players.length / 2) && parseInt(players.length) >= 20">
                                                <td :colspan="displayFields.length"><content-ad :vertical_ad=true :container_element="'roster-players'"  ></content-ad></td>
                                                                </tr>
                                        </template>
                                                        </tbody>
                                                    </table>
                                                    <div class="sidearm-roster-staff-dfp" v-reapplyKnockout>
                                    <ads-component params="{name : 'dfp-leaderboard-standard'}" ></ads-component>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                        `,
                        data: () => ({
                            activeField: null,
                        }),
                        props: {
                            displayFields: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Array,
                            },
                            players: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Array,
                            },
                            sport: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Object,
                            }
                        },
                        computed: {
                            playersSorted() {
                                if (!this.activeField) return this.players;
                                const [field, dir] = this.activeField;
                                if (!this.fieldMap()[field]) return this.players;
                                const sortKeys = this.fieldMap()[field].sort_keys.reverse();
                                return sortKeys.reduce((players, key) => [ ...players.sort(this.compareByKey(key, dir))], [ ...this.players ]);
                            }
                        },
                        methods: {
                            fieldMap(player = {}) {
                                return {
                                    player_firstname: {
                                        display_value: `<a href="/sports/${this.sport.global_sport_name_slug}/roster/${this.slugify(player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name)}/${player.rp_id}" title="${player.first_name}">${player.first_name}</a>`,
                                        sort_keys: ['first_name'],
                                    },
                                    player_lastname: {
                                        display_value: `<a href="/sports/${this.sport.global_sport_name_slug}/roster/${this.slugify(player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name)}/${player.rp_id}" title="${player.last_name}">${player.last_name}</a>`,
                                        sort_keys: ['last_name'],
                                    },
                                    player_hometown: {
                                        display_value: player.hometown,
                                        sort_keys: ['hometown'],
                                    },
                                    player_highschool: {
                                        display_value: player.highschool,
                                        sort_keys: ['highschool'],
                                    },
                                    fullname: {
                                        display_value: `<a href="/sports/${this.sport.global_sport_name_slug}/roster/${this.slugify(player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name)}/${player.rp_id}" title="${player.first_name} ${player.last_name}">${player.first_name} ${player.last_name}</a>`,
                                        sort_keys: ['last_name'],
                                    },
                                    fullname_reverse: {
                                        display_value: `<a href="/sports/${this.sport.global_sport_name_slug}/roster/${this.slugify(player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name)}/${player.rp_id}" title="${player.last_name} ${player.first_name}">${player.last_name} ${player.first_name}</a>`,
                                        sort_keys: ['last_name'],
                                    },
                                    hometownhighschool: {
                                        display_value: `${player.hometown} / ${player.highschool}`,
                                        sort_keys: ['hometown', 'highschool'],
                                    },
                                    rp_position_short: {
                                        display_value: player.position_short,
                                        sort_keys: ['position_short'],
                                    },
                                    rp_position_long: {
                                        display_value: player.position_long,
                                        sort_keys: ['position_long'],
                                    },
                                    height: {
                                        display_value: `${player.height_feet}' ${player.height_inches}"`,
                                        sort_keys: ['height_feet', 'height_inches'],
                                    },
                                    rp_weight: {
                                        display_value: player.weight,
                                        sort_keys: ['weight'],
                                    },
                                    rp_captain: {
                                        display_value: player.is_captain ? '*' : '',
                                        sort_keys: ['is_captain'],
                                    },
                                    rp_custom1: {
                                        display_value: player.custom1,
                                        sort_keys: ['custom1'],
                                    },
                                    rp_custom2: {
                                        display_value: player.custom2,
                                        sort_keys: ['custom2'],
                                    },
                                    rp_custom3: {
                                        display_value: player.custom3,
                                        sort_keys: ['custom3'],
                                    },
                                    image_combined_path: {
                                        display_value: player.image != null ? `<img src="${player.image.path}/${player.image.filename}" alt="${player.image.alt}" >` : "",
                                        sort_keys: '',
                                    },
                                    // fullname_letters: {
                                    //     display_value: `${player.first_name} ${player.last_name} ${player.letters}`,
                                    //     sort_keys: ['first_name', 'last_name', 'letters'],
                                    // },
                                    // rp_letters: {
                                    //     display_value: player.letters.toString(),
                                    //     sort_keys: ['letters'],
                                    // },
                                    player_previous_school: {
                                        display_value: player.previous_school,
                                        sort_keys: ['previous_school'],
                                    },
                                    player_major: {
                                        display_value: player.major,
                                        sort_keys: ['major'],
                                    },
                                    player_facebook_username: {
                                        display_value: player.facebook_username,
                                        sort_keys: ['facebook_username'],
                                    },
                                    player_instagram_username: {
                                        display_value: player.instagram_username,
                                        sort_keys: ['instagram_username'],
                                    },
                                    player_twitter_username: {
                                        display_value: player.twitter_username,
                                        sort_keys: ['twitter_username'],
                                    },
                                    // rp_letters_string: {
                                    //     display_value: player.letters.toString(),
                                    //     sort_keys: ['letters'],
                                    // },
                                    player_birthdate: {
                                        display_value: player.birthdate != null ? player.birthdate.toString() : '',
                                        sort_keys: ['birthdate'],
                                    },
                                    hometownprevious: {
                                        display_value: `${player.hometown} ${player.previous_school}`,
                                        sort_keys: ['hometown', 'previous_school'],
                                    },
                                    roster_jerseynum: {
                                        display_value: player.jersey_number,
                                        sort_keys: ['jersey_number'],
                                    },
                                    roster_class: {
                                        display_value: player.academic_year_short,
                                        sort_keys: ['academic_year_short'],
                                    },
                                    default: {
                                        display_value: '',
                                        sort_keys: '',
                                    },
                                };
                            },
                            getPlayerFieldValue(player, field) {
                                if (!player || !field) return;
                                return this.fieldMap(player)[field].display_value;
                            },
                            slugify(text) {
                                return text.toString().toLowerCase()
                                    .replace(/\s+/g, '-')
                                    .replace(/[^\w\-]+/g, '')
                                    .replace(/\-\-+/g, '-')
                                    .replace(/^-+/, '')
                                    .replace(/-+$/, '');
                            },
                            sortByField(field) {
                                if (!field) return;
                                if (this.activeField && this.activeField[0] === field) {
                                    const [field, dir] = this.activeField;
                                    if (dir === 'desc') this.activeField = null;
                                    else this.activeField = [ field, 'desc' ];
                                }
                                else this.activeField = [ field, 'asc' ];
                            },
                            compareByKey(key, dir) {
                                return (a, b) => {
                                    const _a = this.isNumeric(a[key]) ? parseInt(a[key]) : a[key];
                                    const _b = this.isNumeric(b[key]) ? parseInt(b[key]) : b[key];
                                    if (_a > _b) return (dir === 'asc') ? 1 : -1;
                                    else if (_a < _b) return (dir === 'asc') ? -1 : 1;
                                    return 0;
                                };
                            },
                            isNumeric(str) {
                                if (typeof str != "string") return false;
                                return !isNaN(str) && !isNaN(parseFloat(str));
                            }
                        }
                    });
                    Vue.component('vue-roster-template-cards', {
                        template: `
                            <div class="sidearm-roster-template-cards">
                                <ul class="sidearm-roster-list reset-list flex-column flex medium-flex-row" id="roster-players">
                                    <template v-for="(player, index) in computedPlayers" :key="player.rp_id">
                                        <li  class="sidearm-roster-list-item">
                                            <a class="sidearm-roster-list-item-link flex flex-column" :href="'/sports/' + sport.global_sport_name_slug + '/roster/' + slugify(player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name) + '/' + player.rp_id" :title="player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name">
                                                <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-media">
                                                    <img v-if="player.image" class="sidearm-roster-list-item-photo-img" :src="player.image.path + '/' + player.image.filename + '?width=400&height=400&mode=crop&anchor=topcenter'" :alt="player.image.alt">
                                                    <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-number flex flex-align-center flex-justify-center" v-if="(player.jersey_number || player.jersey_number_2) && checkDisplayFields('roster_jerseynum', 'special_column')">{{ player.jersey_number_2 ? player.jersey_number_2 : player.jersey_number }}</div>
                                                    <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-name">{{ player.first_name + ' ' + player.last_name }}</div>
                                                    </div>
                                                <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-details flex-item-1">
                                                    <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-meta">
                                                        <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-position" v-if="player.position_short && checkDisplayFields('rp_position_short', 'db_field')">{{ player.position_short }}</span>
                                                        <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-position" v-if="player.position_long && checkDisplayFields('rp_position_long', 'db_field')">{{ player.position_long }}</span>
                                                        <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-height" v-if="player.height_feet && player.height_inches && checkDisplayFields('height', 'db_field')">{{ player.height_feet + "'" + ' ' + player.height_inches + '"' }}</span>
                                                        <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-weight" v-if="player.weight && player.gender != 'W' && checkDisplayFields('rp_weight', 'db_field')">{{ player.weight }}</span>
                                                        
                                                </div>
                                                    <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-meta">
                                                        <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-year" v-if="player.academic_year_short && checkDisplayFields('roster_class', 'special_column')">{{ player.academic_year_short }}</span>
                                                        <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-custom3" v-if="player.custom3 && checkDisplayFields('rp_custom3','db_field')">{{ player.custom3 }}</span>
                                                        <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-major" v-if="player.major && checkDisplayFields('player_major','db_field')">{{ player.major }}</span>
                                                        <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-hometown" v-if="player.hometown && (checkDisplayFields('player_hometown','db_field') || checkDisplayFields('hometownhighschool','db_field') || checkDisplayFields('hometownprevious','db_field'))">{{ player.hometown }}</span>
                                                        <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-highschool" v-if="player.highschool && (checkDisplayFields('player_highschool','db_field') || checkDisplayFields('hometownhighschool','db_field'))">{{ player.highschool }}</span>
                                                        <span class="sidearm-roster-list-item-previous-school" v-if="player.previous_school && (checkDisplayFields('player_previous_school','db_field') || checkDisplayFields('hometownprevious','db_field'))">{{ player.previous_school }}</span>
                                                                </div>
                                                <div class="sidearm-roster-list-item-social flex flex-justify-center" v-if="player.has_social_links">
                                                    <a :href="'https://www.twitter.com/' + player.twitter_username" v-if="player.twitter_username">
                                                    <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-twitter sidearm-icon">
                                                    </span></a>
                                                    <a :href="'https://www.instagram.com/' + player.instagram_username" v-if="player.instagram_username">
                                                    <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-instagram sidearm-icon">
                                                    </span></a>
                                                    <a :href="'https://www.youtube.com/' + player.youtube_username" v-if="player.youtube_username">
                                                    <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-youtube sidearm-icon">
                                                    </span></a>
                                                    <a :href="'https://www.twitch.com/' + player.twitch_username" v-if="player.twitch">
                                                    <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-twitch sidearm-icon">
                                                    </span></a>
                                                    <a :href="'https://www.facebook.com/' + player.facebook_username" v-if="player.facebook_username">
                                                    <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-facebook sidearm-icon">
                                                    </span></a>
                                                    <a :href="'https://www.tiktok.com/@' + player.tiktok_username" v-if="player.tiktok_username">
                                                    <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-tiktok sidearm-icon">
                                                    </span></a>
                                                    <a :href="'https://www.cameo.com/' + player.cameo_username" v-if="player.cameo_username">
                                                    <span aria-hidden="true" class="sf-cameo sidearm-icon">
                                                    </span></a>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                            </a>

										                        </li>
                                        <div id="vue-content-ad" v-if="(index + 1) === parseInt(players.length / 2)">
                                            <content-ad :vertical_ad=true :container_element="'roster-players'"  >
                                                            </div>

                                    </template>
									                        </ul>
                                <div class="sidearm-roster-staff-dfp" v-reapplyKnockout>
                                    <ads-component params="{name : 'dfp-leaderboard-standard'}" ></ads-component>
                                                        </div>
                                                            </div>
                        `,
                        props: {
                            displayFields: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Array,
                            },
                            players: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Array,
                            },
                            sport: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Object,
                            }
                        },
                        methods: {
                            checkDisplayFields(field, column_name) {
                                let _field = this.displayFields.find(f => f[column_name] === field)

                                if (_field) {
                                    return true;
                                }

                                return false;
                            },
                            slugify(text) {
                                return text.toString().toLowerCase()
                                    .replace(/\s+/g, '-')
                                    .replace(/[^\w\-]+/g, '')
                                    .replace(/\-\-+/g, '-')
                                    .replace(/^-+/, '')
                                    .replace(/-+$/, '');
                            },
                        },
                        computed: {
                            computedPlayers(){

                                return this.players.map(player => ({ ...player, has_social_links: player.cameo_username || player.facebook_username || player.instagram_username || player.snapchat_username || player.tiktok_username || player.twitch_username || player.youtube_username || false })) 

                            }
                        }
                    });
                    Vue.component('vue-roster-staff', {
                        template: `
                            <div class="sidearm-roster-staff" id="roster-staff">
                                <div class="sidearm-roster-staff-container">
                                    <h3 class="sidearm-roster-staff-section-title">{{ isSupport ? 'Support Staff' : 'Coaches' }}</h3>
                                    <ul class="sidearm-roster-staff-list reset-list flex flex-column medium-flex-row medium-flex-wrap">
                                        <li class="sidearm-roster-staff-item" v-for="(member, index) in staff" :key="member.id">
                                            <a
                                                class="sidearm-roster-staff-link flex flex-align-center"
                                                :href="getStaffLink(member)"
                                                :title="member.firstname + ' ' + member.lastname"
                                            >
                                                <div class="sidearm-roster-staff-image" v-if="member.image && member.image.fullpath">
                                                    <img :src="member.image.fullpath + '?height=96&width=96&mode=crop&anchor=topcenter'" :alt="member.image.alt" >
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="sidearm-roster-staff-details flex-item-1">
                                                    <div class="sidearm-roster-staff-name">{{ member.firstname }} {{ member.lastname }}</div>
                                                    <div class="sidearm-roster-staff-title" v-html="member.title"></div>
                                                        </div>
                                                                </a>
                                                    </li>
                                            </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        `,
                        props: {
                            staff: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Array
                            },
                            sport: {
                                required: true,
                                type: Object
                            },
                            isSupport: {
                                type: Boolean,
                                default: false
                            }
                        },
                        methods: {
                            slugify(text) {
                                return text.toString().toLowerCase()
                                    .replace(/\s+/g, '-')
                                    .replace(/[^\w\-]+/g, '')
                                    .replace(/\-\-+/g, '-')
                                    .replace(/^-+/, '')
                                    .replace(/-+$/, '');
                            },
                            getStaffLink(member) {
                                let rootPath = this.isSupport ? 'roster/staff' : 'roster/coaches';
                                return `/sports/${this.sport.global_sport_name_slug}/${rootPath}/${this.slugify(member.firstname + ' ' + member.lastname)}/${member.id}`;
                            },
                        },
                                });
                    Vue.directive('reapplyKnockout', {
                        inserted: function (el) {
                            var intervalCounter = 0;
                            var interval = setInterval(function () {
                                if (intervalCounter < 50) {
                                    if (ko.dataFor(document.getElementsByTagName('body')[0])) {
                                        clearInterval(interval);
                                        ko.applyBindings({}, el);
                                    }
                                    intervalCounter++;
                                } else {
                                    clearInterval(interval);
                                }
                            }, 100);
                        }
                                });

                            selected_template: null,
                            loading: false,
                            downloadsListActive: false,
                            templates: [
                                {
                                    id: 1,
                                    label: 'Roster View - List',
                                },
                                {
                                    id: 2,
                                    label: 'Roster View - Grid',
                                },
                                {
                                    id: 3,
                                    label: 'Roster View - Cards',
                                    }
                            ]
                        }),
                        methods: {
                            changeSeason(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                let dropdown = document.getElementById("sidearm-roster-select-season");
                                let value = dropdown.options[dropdown.selectedIndex].value;
                                
                                if (!value) return;

                                window.location.replace(value);
                            },
                            changeTemplate(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                let dropdown = document.getElementById("sidearm-roster-select-template");
                                let value = dropdown.options[dropdown.selectedIndex].value;

                                if (!value) return;

                                this.selected_template = parseInt(value);

                                Analytics.trackPageView(window.location.pathname);


                            },
                            getTemplate() {
                                this.selected_template = parseInt(this.roster.template_id);
                            },
                            toggleSearch() {
                                this.search_toggled = !this.search_toggled;

                                if (this.search_toggled) {
                                    this.$refs.roster_search.focus();
                                        }
                            },
                            activateDownloadsList() {
                                this.downloadsListActive = !this.downloadsListActive;
                                }
                        },
                        computed: {
                            jerseyNumbers() {
                                return this.roster.players.some(player => player.jersey_number && player.jersey_number != "");
                            },
                            playersSorted() {
                                let _players = [...this.roster.players];

                                if (this.roster.sort_alpha || !this.jerseyNumbers) {
                                    _players.sort((a, b) => {
                                        if (a.last_name.toLowerCase() > b.last_name.toLowerCase()) return 1;
                                        else if (a.last_name.toLowerCase() < b.last_name.toLowerCase()) return -1;
                                        return 0;
                                    });
                                } else {
                                    _players.sort((a, b) => (parseInt(a.jersey_number) > parseInt(b.jersey_number)) ? 1 : -1);
                                }

                                if (this.roster.order_rosters_by_women_first) {
                                    _players.sort((a, b) => {
                                        if (a.gender > b.gender) return 1;
                                        else if (a.gender < b.gender) return -1;
                                        return 0;
                            });
                                } else {
                                    _players.sort((a, b) => {
                                        if (a.gender > b.gender) return -1;
                                        else if (a.gender < b.gender) return 1;
                                        return 0;
			                            });
			                        }

                                if (this.search_query != '') {
                                    let query = this.search_query.toLowerCase().trim();

                                    return _players.filter(player => {
                                        let name = `${player.first_name.toLowerCase()} ${player.last_name.toLowerCase()}`
                                        return name.includes(query);
			                    });
                                } else {
                                    return _players;
			                }
                            },
                            templateName() {
                                if (this.selected_template === 2) {
                                    return 'vue-roster-template-grid';
                                } else if (this.selected_template === 3) {
                                    return 'vue-roster-template-cards';
                                } else {
                                    return 'vue-roster-template-list';
			                }
			                }
                        },
                        created() {
                            this.getTemplate();
                                    }
                                });
                        });
                    </script>
		

        
            <script src="./2021-22 Men&#39;s Basketball Roster - Iowa State University Athletics_files/ISUAC"></script>
         
			</main>

                <h2 class="hide" id="h2_sponsors">Sponsors</h2>
                <div class="s-sponsors__row row pad">

            <script>
                require(['jquery', 'jquery-ui', 'headroom', 'jquery-headroom'], function($) {
                    $(window).on("load, resize", function(){

                        //Initalize headroom with proper offsets that is triggered only when the viewport is resized rather than onscroll
                        var offset_height = $('.main-header__sticky').outerHeight();
                        $('html').headroom('destroy').removeData('headroom').headroom({offset: offset_height});
                        }).trigger('resize'); 

                    $(function(){
                        $('.s-events__wrapper').tabs();
                        window.triggerTabs = function(init) {
                            init = init || 0;
                            $('.s-events__wrapper').tabs({ active: init });
                        };
                        window.triggerTabs(0);
                    }); 

                    $('body').on('click', '.main-header__offcanvas-toggle', function(e){
                        e.preventDefault();
                        $('html').toggleClass('mobile-calendar-open');
                        
                        ko.contextFor($('.c-navigation--main')[0]).$component.closeMenu();
                        ko.contextFor($('.c-navigation--sport')[0]).$component.closeMenu();
                    });

                    $( document ).ready(function() {
                        // First we get the viewport height and we multiple it by 1% to get a value for a vh unit
                        let vh = window.innerHeight * 0.01;
                        // Then we set the value in the --vh custom property to the root of the document
                        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--vh', `${vh}px`);
                    });
                });
            </script>

                    // We execute the same script as before
                    let vh = window.innerHeight * 0.01;
                    document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--vh', `${vh}px`);
                });

                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return 0;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if(model.component.name != 'main-nav')
                                        return 0;
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav')
                                        return model.isMenuOpen() ? '0' : '-1';
                                    return 0;
                                })
                            },
                            event: {
                                focus: function() {
                                    var index =

                                    if(index < 0)

                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav') {
                                        model.openMenu();
                                    }
                                    return;
                                },

                                    var index =

                                        model.closeMenu();

                                    return;

                    <script>
                        window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = true;

                        require(['knockout'], function (ko) {
                            function register_custom_loader(component, vm_name, template_name) {
                                if (document.getElementById('template-' + (template_name || component) )) {
                                    var custom_loader = {
                                        getConfig: function(name, callback) {
                                            if (name === component + '-component') {
                                                componentConfig = {
                                                    template: { element: 'template-' + (template_name || component) },
                                                    viewModel: { require: 'components/' + (vm_name || component) }
                                                };
                                                callback(componentConfig);
                                            }
                                            else {
                                                callback(null)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    };

                                    ko.components.loaders.unshift(custom_loader);
                                }
                            }

                            register_custom_loader('ads', 'promotions', 'promotions');
                            register_custom_loader('dfp', 'evergreen', 'evergreen');

                            register_custom_loader('navigation');
register_custom_loader('events');
register_custom_loader('results');
register_custom_loader('search');

                            
                            window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = false;
                        });
                    </script>

<script type="text/x-template" id="widgets-videos-related-template">
<div class="sa-widgets-videos-related"  :class="is_medium_up ? 'sa-widgets-stories-related--medium' : ''">
    <header class="sa-widgets-videos-related__header">

        </div>
    </header>
    <ul class="reset-list sa-widgets-videos-related__items">

                    <div class="sa-widgets-videos-related__item-media-container">
                        <div class="sa-widgets-videos-related__item-media-inner">
                            <img  class="sa-widgets-videos-related__item-media" :src="item.video_thumbnail_url" :alt="item.video_title" />

            </article>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <a class="sa-widgets-videos-related__more-link sa-widgets-videos-related__more-link--footer" href="/watch">More in Videos <span class="sa-widgets-videos-related__more-icon sf-arrows-circle-right"></span></a>

    <div v-show="selected_video"  class="sa-widgets-videos-related__modal" role="dialog" aria-label="Watch selected video" v-focus-trap-within:['updates']>
        <div class="sa-widgets-videos-related__modal-inner flex flex-column flex-align-stretch" >
            <div class="sa-widgets-videos-related__modal-player-wrapper">
                <div class="sa-widgets-videos-related__modal-player">
                     <iframe :src="selected_video_embed_url" class="showcase-video-player"></iframe>
                </div>

        <button type="button" class="sa-widgets-videos-related__modal-close"  @click="toggle_video(false)" aria-label="Close video modal">

<script>
    require(['vue', 'moment', 'widgets-mixin'], function (Vue, moment, WidgetsMixin) {
        Vue.prototype.moment = moment;
        var setFocusTrapListeners = function(el, binding, node, oldVnode) {
            var focusable_elements = 'button, [href], input, select, textarea, [tabindex]:not([tabindex="-1"])';
            
            var selector = binding.value;
    
            var target_element = selector ? document.querySelector(selector) : el;
            if (!target_element) return;
    
            var focusable_elements_in_target = target_element.querySelectorAll(focusable_elements);
            if (!focusable_elements_in_target.length) return;
    
            var first_element_in_target = focusable_elements_in_target[0];
            var last_element_in_target = focusable_elements_in_target[focusable_elements_in_target.length - 1];
    
            first_element_in_target.removeEventListener('keydown', focus_last_element);
            last_element_in_target.removeEventListener('keydown', focus_first_element);
    
            first_element_in_target.addEventListener('keydown', focus_last_element);
            last_element_in_target.addEventListener('keydown', focus_first_element);


            function focus_first_element(event) {
                if (event.key === 'Tab' && !event.shiftKey) {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    first_element_in_target.focus();
                }
            }

            function focus_last_element(event) {
                if (event.key === 'Tab' && event.shiftKey) {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    last_element_in_target.focus();
                }
            }
        }

       Vue.component('widgets-videos-related', {
           template: '#widgets-videos-related-template',
           props: ['params'],
            mixins:[WidgetsMixin],
            data: function () {
                return {
                    raw_data:  [],
                    hostname: window.location.host,
                    selected_video: false,
                }
            },
           directives: {
               focusTrapWithin: {
                   inserted: setFocusTrapListeners,

                   componentUpdated: function (el, binding) {
                       if (binding.arg === 'updates') {
                           setFocusTrapListeners(el, binding);
                       }
                   }
               }
           },
           computed: {
                component_data: function() {
                    if (this.raw_data) {
                        let _data = this.raw_data.slice();
                        return _data;
                    } else {
                        return null;
                    }
               },
               selected_video_embed_url: function () {
                   if (this.selected_video) {

                       let _type = this.selected_video.video_type == "all-access" ? "Archive" : "youtube";
                       let _id =this.selected_video.video_type == "all-access" ?  this.selected_video.video_id : this.selected_video.video_url;
                       return window.location.protocol + "//" + window.location.host + "/showcase/embed.aspx?" + _type + "=" +_id + "&autoplay=true";
                   } else {
                       return '';
                   }
               }
            },
           methods: {
               toggle_video: function (state) {
                   this.selected_video = state;

                   if (this.selected_video) {
                      this.$el.querySelector('.sa-widgets-videos-related__modal-close').focus();
                   }
               }
           },
           created() {
               this.raw_data = window.sidearmWidgets[this.params].data;
           }
       });
        
        var instance = new Vue({
            el: '#sa-widgets-c50d12c4-87df-45b2-a1d9-e63b9dc045d0'
        });
        
    });
</script>

                return { 
                }
            }
        });

        });
        
    });
</script>

<script type="text/x-template" id="widgets-stories-related-template">
    <div class="sa-widgets-stories-related" :class="is_medium_up ? 'sa-widgets-stories-related--medium' : ''">
        <header class="sa-widgets-stories-related__header">
            <div class="flex flex-align-end flex-justify-between">
                <h2 class="sa-widgets-stories-related__title">Related News</h2>
                <div class="sa-widgets-stories-related__ad"  v-reapply_knockout>
                    <ads-component params="{name : 'cs-related-stories-content-module'}" ></ads-component>
                </div>
                <a class="sa-widgets-stories-related__more-link sa-widgets-stories-related__more-link--header" :href="archive_link">More in News <span class="sa-widgets-stories-related__more-icon sf-arrows-circle-right"></span></a>
            </div>
        </header>
        <ul class="reset-list sa-widgets-stories-related__items">
            <li class="sa-widgets-stories-related__item" v-for="item in component_data" :key="item.title">
                <article class="sa-widgets-stories-related__item-article">
                    <a class="sa-widgets-stories-related__item-url  flex flex-align-start" :href="item.url">
                        <div class="sa-widgets-stories-related__item-media-container">
                            <div class="sa-widgets-stories-related__item-media-inner">
                                <div  class="sa-widgets-stories-related__item-media flex flex-justify-center flex-align-start">
                                <img v-if="item.image_source"  :src="item.image_source + image_settings" :alt="item.image_alt_text" />
                                <img v-else :src="custom_cdn + '/images/logos/site/site.png?width=352&height=198&mode=pad&scale=canvas&bgcolor=f5f5f5&anchor=center&s.grayscale=flat'" alt=""/>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sa-widgets-stories-related__item-content">
                            <h3 class="sa-widgets-stories-related__item-title">
                                {{ item.title }}
                            </h3>
                            <time class="sa-widgets-stories-related__item-time" datetime="item.date">{{moment(item.date).fromNow()}}</time>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </article>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <a class="sa-widgets-stories-related__more-link sa-widgets-stories-related__more-link--footer" :href="archive_link">More in News <span class="sa-widgets-stories-related__more-icon sf-arrows-circle-right"></span></a>
    </div>
</script>
<script>
    require(['vue', 'moment','widgets-mixin'], function (Vue, moment, WidgetsMixin) {
        Vue.prototype.moment = moment;
        Vue.component('widgets-stories-related', {
            template: '#widgets-stories-related-template',
            props: ['params'],
            mixins:[WidgetsMixin],
            data: function () {
                return {
                    raw_data: {},
                    hostname: window.location.host,
                    custom_cdn: '' 
                }
            },
            computed: {
                component_data: function () {
                    return this.raw_data.data;
                },
                archive_link: function () {
                    return window.associated_sport ? '/sports/' + window.associated_sport.shortname + '/archives' : '/archives';
                },
                image_settings: function () {
                    return this.is_medium_up ? '?width=352&height=198&mode=crop&scale=both&format=jpg&quality=80' : '?width=60&height=60&mode=crop&scale=both&format=jpg&quality=80';
                }
            },
            created() {
                this.raw_data = window.sidearmWidgets[this.params];
                this.custom_cdn = window.sidearmWidgets[this.params].extra.custom_cdn;
            }
        });

        
        var instance = new Vue({
            el: '#sa-widgets-a5f44bce-faa9-4610-9224-53bd74d3771a'
        });
        
    });
</script>

<script>
    var host_element = document.querySelector(".b0q4pzjg1-modal__text-host");
    host_element.href = window.location.href; 
    host_element.innerText = window.location.hostname; 

    function close_banner() {
        var CookieDate = new Date;
        CookieDate.setTime(CookieDate.getTime() + 1 * 3600 * 1000 * 24);
        document.cookie = "sidearm-adblock-banner_consent=true; expires=\"" + CookieDate.toGMTString() + "\";";
        document.querySelector(".b0q4pzjg1").remove();
    }

    var consent_button = document.querySelector(".b0q4pzjg1-banner__consent");

    consent_button.addEventListener("click", function() { close_banner(); });

    require(['config'], function(config) {
        require(['jquery', 'knockout', 'cookie', 'text'], function ($, ko, cookie, text) {
            $(function () {   
                //disable check for Siteimprove scans
                if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('siteimprove') < 0) {
                    
                    if (cookie.get_cookie('sidearm-adblock-banner_consent')) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var deferred = $.Deferred();
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "HEAD",
                        async: true,
                        url: "/components/js/analytics.js",
                    }).done(function(message,text,jqXHR){
                        deferred.resolve();
                    })
                    .fail(function(err){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                        deferred.reject();
                    });

                    deferred.then(function(success) {
                        $.get('/common/templates/dfp/dfp-component-template.html')
                            .then(function (response) {
                            }, function (error) {
                                show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                            });
                    }, function (error) {
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    })
                    .fail(function(){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    });

                    function show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal() {
                        var modal = document.querySelector('.b0q4pzjg1');
                        modal.style.display = 'flex';
                        modal.querySelector('.b0q4pzjg1-banner__consent').focus();
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>
